{"tid":2312797,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"李臻：沒受過教育的人愛批鬥大學生，香港似足文革 !","createTime":"2020-12-05T09:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T03:45:06.000Z","uid":219007,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fcf5a20d61478923afc905ba830479bfd92d07f0","tid":2312797,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T09:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://news.memehk.com/img/post/9480_675.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fimg%2Fpost%2F9480_675.jpg&h=fc8685c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前香港大學校委會維持「等埋首席副校」再任命副校長後，學生衝入會議現場。其中一名校委會成員李國章批評大學生行為如同「文革」。資深新聞工作者李臻於其Facebook 反指香港最似文革的地方，就是一班沒受過教育的人愛批鬥大學生。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n李國章於學生衝入校委會會議後，批評大學生如同紅衛兵，「文化大革命剛開始時，紅衛兵的做法並沒有如後期般誇張，但那就是他們如何開展大革命的模樣。他們驅逐教授、強逼他們坐下、下跪承認他們做錯了。」形容事件完全是歷史重演。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前有線、無綫新聞記者及主播，現任now寬頻電視首席主播李臻，在其Facebook回應此事，他指「香港現時最似文化大革命的地方，可能是愈來愈多沒有受過太多教育和不太識字的人，愛批評 / 批鬥大學生和知識分子。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.memehk.com/posts/9480?fb_comment_id=1018970314809942_1019155511458089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fposts%2F9480%3Ffb_comment_id%3D1018970314809942_1019155511458089&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w%2BzsNYmc6RwURZU94nRINXI%3D&h=52f2a717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.memehk.com/posts/9480?fb_comment_id=1018970314809942_1019155511458089</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">2015@李臻</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"08cfd65956cc9b437835ef594bf17464e54aa485","tid":2312797,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T09:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c85970dec60c6e2f6d8ee752ba5e25af8fbd264","tid":2312797,"uid":171107,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T09:19:10.000Z","msg":"批判警務人員，犯国安法"},{"pid":"c5ddce4df11c1735ffd77663feedac08cc973e28","tid":2312797,"uid":130177,"like":0,"disl